{"tw": {"3521270": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Phoenix's Faye.飞儿", "steam_appid": 3521270, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/8350e692606ea77bc94a8efe1ea30a3a.poster.avif?t=1766593505\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/8350e692606ea77bc94a8efe1ea30a3a.webm?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/8350e692606ea77bc94a8efe1ea30a3a.mp4?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>這是我一個人用虛幻引擎開發的遊戲，故事背景：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一位自幼習武的姑娘，精通劍術、箭術，拳腳功夫了得！不知何故，陷入一個奇幻世界。她需要不斷地戰鬥，找到回家之路！這個奇幻世界不同的地方風格各異，有武俠風、仙俠風、暗黑風等等，在不同的風格的地域挑戰不同的敵人，享受戰鬥的樂趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新角色</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/6262a7036a0699fcefdf0091bd0c1978.avif?t=1766593505\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/2b2ba9a5f0057ef4103cd019e498a6f9.avif?t=1766593505\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新增爆衣系統</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/75d9905af826ae4ab212622a7bba9aae.poster.avif?t=1766593505\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/75d9905af826ae4ab212622a7bba9aae.webm?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/75d9905af826ae4ab212622a7bba9aae.mp4?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>新增手殘難度（簡單難度）！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在選項中可以設定簡單難度，遊戲中也可以隨時切換難度。不用擔心，簡單難度下敵人不會變弱智，但玩家只要多做騷操作，如彈反、完美閃避等，就可以大量回血，並且火力值更容易充滿，隨時可以爆大招！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>彈反、完美閃避難做出來嗎？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這可能是最容易做出彈反和完美閃避的動作遊戲了，遊戲判斷相當寬鬆，玩家可以風騷地閃閃閃、彈彈彈！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>遊戲有點難度！</strong>（別擔心，有手殘難度幫你）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲有些難度，並且操作方式上與其他ACT不太一樣：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1）不需要手動鎖定敵人，鎖定後反而不好打。遊戲有自動索敵系統，會根據敵人的位置、玩家的移動方向等自動「黏住」你想進攻或防禦的敵人，方便在群戰中左一刀右一刀地「砍瓜切菜」。當你特別需要針對某個敵人時，才需要手動鎖定。射箭時不要用鎖定功能哈，鎖定後反而不好瞄準。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2）需要解鎖合適的技能來應對群戰，強烈建議武士刀的「圓月彎刀」，完美閃避時按攻擊鍵，可以劃出一道完美弧圈，大面積殺傷敵人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲中的新手村一定要先完成哈，不僅能了解基本操作，還可以獲得300靈石。還有遊戲中的技能表也要多去看看，在開始界面和暫停菜單中都可以查看「角色與技能」。遊玩「刀光劍影」關卡時，多留意左上方的提示。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我專門製作了保姆式入門攻略，對遊戲感興趣的小夥伴一定要看看哈，點右側的「查看手冊」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/91b127563f05a7486b61dc8d538380a7.poster.avif?t=1766593505\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/91b127563f05a7486b61dc8d538380a7.webm?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/91b127563f05a7486b61dc8d538380a7.mp4?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>「刀光劍影」關卡特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >女主角將會面對劍兵、盾兵和弓箭手等多種兵種的圍攻，這是一場真正意義上的群毆，並非多人圍觀只有一人上前的那種，而是不講武德、全部一擁而上的戰鬥！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >女主角可以使用太刀迎敵，也可以切換為弓箭，甚至赤手空拳上陣。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用太刀面對多人圍攻時，主要技巧是「彈反」和「完美閃避」。成功彈反可以彈開攻擊的敵人，而在完美閃避的瞬間發動攻擊，太刀會劃出一道漂亮的圓弧。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直接使用拳腳功夫往往能產生奇效。在這個奇幻世界裡，你可以施展「隔山打牛拳」和「穿心腿」等招式，一舉擊倒大片敵人。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲中沒有拾取血包的機制，而是透過做出超酷的動作（例如：彈反、完美閃避等）來恢復生命值，同時還能積攢「火力槽」。當火力槽蓄滿後，即可發動強力的大範圍攻擊，一口氣擊倒眾多敵人！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>還有更多關卡等著你挑戰！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/31616f8e9a942ba11652ace17880dee2.poster.avif?t=1766593505\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/31616f8e9a942ba11652ace17880dee2.webm?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/31616f8e9a942ba11652ace17880dee2.mp4?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/3a42c40fb75b54107577a83435a1fd7e.poster.avif?t=1766593505\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/3a42c40fb75b54107577a83435a1fd7e.webm?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/3a42c40fb75b54107577a83435a1fd7e.mp4?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/70dcf5fae8081c65fb8fcff44968f1bd.poster.avif?t=1766593505\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/70dcf5fae8081c65fb8fcff44968f1bd.webm?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/70dcf5fae8081c65fb8fcff44968f1bd.mp4?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/31334f214668f0446b0a8028ebfe76a4.poster.avif?t=1766593505\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/31334f214668f0446b0a8028ebfe76a4.webm?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/31334f214668f0446b0a8028ebfe76a4.mp4?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>麻雀姊姊是這個奇幻世界的傳奇人物，你可以操控她完成她的專屬關卡！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/3fbe8a87ecae9a10c161840a0c439116.poster.avif?t=1766593505\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/3fbe8a87ecae9a10c161840a0c439116.webm?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/3fbe8a87ecae9a10c161840a0c439116.mp4?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p clas