0 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/2b2ba9a5f0057ef4103cd019e498a6f9.avif?t=1766593505\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新增爆衣系統</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/75d9905af826ae4ab212622a7bba9aae.poster.avif?t=1766593505\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/75d9905af826ae4ab212622a7bba9aae.webm?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/75d9905af826ae4ab212622a7bba9aae.mp4?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>新增手殘難度（簡單難度）！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在選項中可以設定簡單難度，遊戲中也可以隨時切換難度。不用擔心，簡單難度下敵人不會變弱智，但玩家只要多做騷操作，如彈反、完美閃避等，就可以大量回血，並且火力值更容易充滿，隨時可以爆大招！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>彈反、完美閃避難做出來嗎？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這可能是最容易做出彈反和完美閃避的動作遊戲了，遊戲判斷相當寬鬆，玩家可以風騷地閃閃閃、彈彈彈！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>遊戲有點難度！</strong>（別擔心，有手殘難度幫你）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲有些難度，並且操作方式上與其他ACT不太一樣：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1）不需要手動鎖定敵人，鎖定後反而不好打。遊戲有自動索敵系統，會根據敵人的位置、玩家的移動方向等自動「黏住」你想進攻或防禦的敵人，方便在群戰中左一刀右一刀地「砍瓜切菜」。當你特別需要針對某個敵人時，才需要手動鎖定。射箭時不要用鎖定功能哈，鎖定後反而不好瞄準。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2）需要解鎖合適的技能來應對群戰，強烈建議武士刀的「圓月彎刀」，完美閃避時按攻擊鍵，可以劃出一道完美弧圈，大面積殺傷敵人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲中的新手村一定要先完成哈，不僅能了解基本操作，還可以獲得300靈石。還有遊戲中的技能表也要多去看看，在開始界面和暫停菜單中都可以查看「角色與技能」。遊玩「刀光劍影」關卡時，多留意左上方的提示。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我專門製作了保姆式入門攻略，對遊戲感興趣的小夥伴一定要看看哈，點右側的「查看手冊」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/91b127563f05a7486b61dc8d538380a7.poster.avif?t=1766593505\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/91b127563f05a7486b61dc8d538380a7.webm?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/91b127563f05a7486b61dc8d538380a7.mp4?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>「刀光劍影」關卡特色：</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >女主角將會面對劍兵、盾兵和弓箭手等多種兵種的圍攻，這是一場真正意義上的群毆，並非多人圍觀只有一人上前的那種，而是不講武德、全部一擁而上的戰鬥！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >女主角可以使用太刀迎敵，也可以切換為弓箭，甚至赤手空拳上陣。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用太刀面對多人圍攻時，主要技巧是「彈反」和「完美閃避」。成功彈反可以彈開攻擊的敵人，而在完美閃避的瞬間發動攻擊，太刀會劃出一道漂亮的圓弧。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直接使用拳腳功夫往往能產生奇效。在這個奇幻世界裡，你可以施展「隔山打牛拳」和「穿心腿」等招式，一舉擊倒大片敵人。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遊戲中沒有拾取血包的機制，而是透過做出超酷的動作（例如：彈反、完美閃避等）來恢復生命值，同時還能積攢「火力槽」。當火力槽蓄滿後，即可發動強力的大範圍攻擊，一口氣擊倒眾多敵人！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>還有更多關卡等著你挑戰！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/31616f8e9a942ba11652ace17880dee2.poster.avif?t=1766593505\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/31616f8e9a942ba11652ace17880dee2.webm?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/31616f8e9a942ba11652ace17880dee2.mp4?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/3a42c40fb75b54107577a83435a1fd7e.poster.avif?t=1766593505\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/3a42c40fb75b54107577a83435a1fd7e.webm?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/3a42c40fb75b54107577a83435a1fd7e.mp4?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/70dcf5fae8081c65fb8fcff44968f1bd.poster.avif?t=1766593505\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/70dcf5fae8081c65fb8fcff44968f1bd.webm?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/70dcf5fae8081c65fb8fcff44968f1bd.mp4?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/31334f214668f0446b0a8028ebfe76a4.poster.avif?t=1766593505\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/31334f214668f0446b0a8028ebfe76a4.webm?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/31334f214668f0446b0a8028ebfe76a4.mp4?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>麻雀姊姊是這個奇幻世界的傳奇人物，你可以操控她完成她的專屬關卡！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/3fbe8a87ecae9a10c161840a0c439116.poster.avif?t=1766593505\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/3fbe8a87ecae9a10c161840a0c439116.webm?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/3fbe8a87ecae9a10c161840a0c439116.mp4?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/60cdfba6ab59a4f37281de3756af48dc.poster.avif?t=1766593505\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/60cdfba6ab59a4f37281de3756af48dc.webm?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/60cdfba6ab59a4f37281de3756af48dc.mp4?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >QQ群：979195753</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >對本遊戲和遊戲開發感興趣的小夥伴，歡迎關注我的嗶哩嗶哩「大火球老師」！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "short_description": "一位自幼習武的姑娘，不知何故陷入了一個奇幻世界。她必須不斷戰鬥，尋找回家的路！如今急需各位大俠出手相救！這是一款高難度的動作遊戲，結合緊湊的戰鬥、沉浸感十足的場景氛圍，以及壓迫感極強的NPC。玩家需根據不同NPC的特性與站位，結合場景特點採取靈活戰術。遊戲鼓勵積極進攻，值得反覆挑戰！", "supported_languages": "英文, 簡體中文, 繁體中文, 俄文, 日文, 法文, 義大利文, 德文, 西班牙文 - 西班牙, 葡萄牙文 - 巴西, 葡萄牙文 - 葡萄牙, 西班牙文 - 拉丁美洲, 越南文, 印尼語, 丹麥文, 烏克蘭文, 保加利亞文, 匈牙利文, 土耳其文, 挪威文, 捷克文, 波蘭文, 瑞典文, 芬蘭文, 羅馬尼亞文, 荷蘭文", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/8872affaaabe868e953103607f3d5f79eed74332/header.jpg?t=1766593505", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/22fbde01cf1832e346680a69ab1fcade96bfbb0c/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1766593505", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/22fbde01cf1832e346680a69ab1fcade96bfbb0c/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1766593505", "website": "https://space.bilibili.com/269589880", "pc_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要 64 位元的處理器及作業系統<br></li><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 10 64-bit<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core i5-8400, AMD Ryzen 5 2600<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 16 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> NVIDIA GeForce GTX 2060 (6GB), AMD Radeon RX 5600 XT<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> 版本：12<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 20 GB 可用空間</li></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>需要 64 位元的處理器及作業系統<br></li><li><strong>作業系統:</strong> Windows 11 64-bit<br></li><li><strong>處理器:</strong> Intel Core i7-13700K, AMD Ryzen 7 7800X3D<br></li><li><strong>記憶體:</strong> 32 GB 記憶體<br></li><li><strong>顯示卡:</strong> NVIDIA GeForce RTX 4070, AMD Radeon RX 7800 XT<br></li><li><strong>DirectX:</strong> 版本：12<br></li><li><strong>儲存空間:</strong> 20 GB 可用空間</li></ul>"}, "mac_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"}, "linux_requirements": {"minimum": "<strong>最低配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>", "recommended": "<strong>建議配備:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"}, "developers": ["BigFireball"], "publishers": ["BigFireball"], "price_overview": {"currency": "TWD", "initial": 18800, "final": 18800, "discount_percent": 0, "initial_formatted": "", "final_formatted": "NT$ 188"}, "categories": [{"id": 2, "description": "單人"}, {"id": 22, "description": "Steam 成就"}, {"id": 28, "description": "完全支援控制器"}, {"id": 66, "description": "顏色替代選項"}, {"id": 74, "description": "遊玩無需快速反應"}, {"id": 23, "description": "Steam 雲端"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "1", "description": "動作"}, {"id": "25", "description": "冒險"}, {"id": "23", "description": "獨立製作"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2025 年 11 月 4 日"}}}}, "us": {"3521270": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "Phoenix's Faye", "steam_appid": 3521270, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "controller_support": "full", "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/8350e692606ea77bc94a8efe1ea30a3a.poster.avif?t=1766593505\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/8350e692606ea77bc94a8efe1ea30a3a.webm?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/8350e692606ea77bc94a8efe1ea30a3a.mp4?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This is a game that I developed alone using Unreal. The story background:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A young woman trained in martial arts since childhood, she masters swordsmanship, archery, and formidable hand-to-hand combat! For some unknown reason, she finds herself trapped in a fantastical world. To return home, she must fight endlessly. This fantastical world features diverse regions, each with its own unique style—wuxia, xianxia, dark fantasy, etc. She battles different enemies across these varied lands, embracing the thrill of combat!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>New Character</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/6262a7036a0699fcefdf0091bd0c1978.avif?t=1766593505\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/2b2ba9a5f0057ef4103cd019e498a6f9.avif?t=1766593505\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Clothing Destruction System</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/75d9905af826ae4ab212622a7bba9aae.poster.avif?t=1766593505\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/75d9905af826ae4ab212622a7bba9aae.webm?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/75d9905af826ae4ab212622a7bba9aae.mp4?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>New &quot;All Thumbs&quot; Difficulty (Easy Mode)!</strong><br>You can enable Easy Mode in the options, and switch difficulties anytime during gameplay. Don't worry—enemies won't become dumb in Easy Mode, but players can regain large amounts of health by performing stylish moves like parries and perfect dodges. Additionally, the special meter fills up more easily, allowing you to unleash powerful moves anytime!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Are parries and perfect dodges hard to execute?</strong><br>This might be the easiest action game to pull off parries and perfect dodges! The game's mechanics are quite lenient, so players can stylishly dodge and parry to their heart's content!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/91b127563f05a7486b61dc8d538380a7.poster.avif?t=1766593505\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/91b127563f05a7486b61dc8d538380a7.webm?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/91b127563f05a7486b61dc8d538380a7.mp4?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>‘Swords &amp; Shadows’ Level Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The heroine faces relentless group battles—swordsmen, shield bearers, archersk, a true swarm combat experience. No polite duels here，enemies rush in all at once, no holds barred!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Switch combat styles on the fly: Wield a tachi, switch to arrows, or go bare-handed，adapt to any threat.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tachi mastery against crowds: Parry to deflect attackers, perfect dodge to counter — each slash carves a gleaming arc through foes.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unarmed? No problem! In this world, martial arts unleash &quot;Mountain-Splitting Strikes&quot; and &quot;Heart-Piercing Kicks&quot; — sending enemies flying in waves.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Forget health packs—style equals survival: Regain HP by nailing parries, dodges, etc. Build the Rage Gauge(Fire), when full, unleash a screen-clearing ultimate attack!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>There are more levels waiting for you to challenge!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/31616f8e9a942ba11652ace17880dee2.poster.avif?t=1766593505\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_