e: @VeryBigFireball</strong></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/8350e692606ea77bc94a8efe1ea30a3a.poster.avif?t=1766593505\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/8350e692606ea77bc94a8efe1ea30a3a.webm?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/8350e692606ea77bc94a8efe1ea30a3a.mp4?t=1766593505\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>This is a game that I developed alone using Unreal. The story background:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A young woman trained in martial arts since childhood, she masters swordsmanship, archery, and formidable hand-to-hand combat! For some unknown reason, she finds herself trapped in a fantastical world. To return home, she must fight endlessly. This fantastical world features diverse regions, each with its own unique style—wuxia, xianxia, dark fantasy, etc. She battles different enemies across these varied lands, embracing the thrill of combat!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>New Character</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/6262a7036a0699fcefdf0091bd0c1978.avif?t=1766593505\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3521270/extras/2b2ba9a5f0057ef4103cd019e498a6f9.avif?t=1766593505\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Clothing Destruction System</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >